CONCEPTS AND KEY DIFF BETWEEN SIMILAR TOPICS
==============================================


| Concept        | Dijkstra                                              | Prim                                                      |
| -------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| Type           | Greedy algorithm                                      | Greedy algorithm                                          |
| Data Structure | Priority Queue / Min Heap                             | Priority Queue / Min Heap                                 |
| Core Action    | Expand the node with **minimum distance from source** | Add the edge with **minimum weight to an unvisited node** |
| Visited Check  | Yes                                                   | Yes                                                       |
| Updates        | Distance to a node from source                        | Cost to connect a node to the MST                         |

Final Analogy:

Dijkstra: Like navigating from one city to all others with the shortest travel time.

Prim: Like building a network of roads to connect all cities with the least construction cost.
